  <summary>6/28/1988--Introduced.
Amends the Federal judicial code to make funds from the Department of Justice Assets Forfeiture Fund available to assist State and local governments in financing construction, expansion, maintenance, and operation of penal facilities. Amends the Tariff Act of 1930 to add a parallel provision with respect to the Customs Forfeiture Fund.</summary>
